title: RB Rankings: 11-20 + Never Not Working, Burnt Salmon - Fantasy Football Podcast for 8/12
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason continue through RB Rankings for the 2021 season! Find out which players have the best chance to be fantasy football league winners! Plus the debut of the “Never Not Working” segment and the latest NFL News. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for August 12th, 2021.
  
 Dominate your fantasy football draft with the 2021 Ultimate Draft Kit -- get the Draft Analyzer with the UDK+
  
 (05:00) - Never Not Working 
 (17:00) - NFL News
 (28:35) - Running Back Rankings Part Two
 (29:30) - Joe Mixon
 (33:35) - Antonio Gibson
 (39:00) - Clyde Edwards-Helaire
 (45:25) - Najee Harris
 (49:30) - David Montgomery
 (53:00) - Chris Carson
 (55:55) - D’Andre Swift
 (58:15) - Josh Jacobs
 (01:00:05) - J.K. Dobbins
